name: Ethel Viola Mellin
bio:
MELLIN In Memory of Ethel Viola Mellin
daughter of Adolph & Susanna Mellin
died Oct, 17, 1884 aged 1 yr. 28 ds.
Not lost, blest thought
But gone before
Where we will meet
To part no more
